{"tid":580646,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係香港做設計真係賤過地底泥！ [sosad]","createTime":"2018-03-04T16:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T17:24:21.000Z","uid":86896,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c426bc22f20a08097b0f4332124bcbe21791267b","tid":580646,"uid":86896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:05:34.000Z","msg":"啲客覺得請你做嘢佢就係上帝 (freelance)<br />\n其實freelance 個客點解會覺得佢係僱主 designer係受僱？ 份design 作品係屬於佢所擁有 ，designer 冇權向外界表示件作品係出自佢手？更吾可以post上網 ？ (當然，除非本身簽左保密協議，或者份嘢未出街啦)<br />\n<br />\nFreelancers其實係屬以自僱人士（self-employed）形式出售服務，並不受僱於任何公司，同合作公司(Project Owner)並無僱傭既關係，<br />\n而屬於一種合作 / 服務交易既關係，Freelancers 同合作公司之間係一個服務交易的合約性質。因此，Freelancers 不會受到《僱傭條例》的保障<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得係受僱 就跟番《僱傭條例》做足番啲嘢！ <br />\n<br />\n覺得比錢，就係買左份嘢，其實只係比錢買個作品既使用權咋！ 吾通係Getty images 買左張相，張相就屬於你？ 只係買黎可以用... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打工一樣慘，左改右改，個design 係跟一個冇讀過design 既人去做出來！ 咁你做得啦，仲搵咩人設計姐！ <br />\n<br />\n所以係香港做designer真係賤過地底泥！ 尤其係平面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以尊重番個designer嗎？"},{"pid":"481870d49b3004885ea084b95b157eb7de423a01","tid":580646,"uid":5309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:06:50.000Z","msg":"吾你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96802ba3d7a451a210047113ceb3a3b5f68a826f","tid":580646,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0999943d20ec3584119bba013b552672ff8b358e","tid":580646,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T17:24:21.000Z","msg":"你自己都